📘 API Testing Guide (Playwright + xUnit + Postgres)
🧠 Overview

This project demonstrates API Testing using Playwright with xUnit.
The goal is to validate backend functionality by sending HTTP requests and verifying responses, without relying on UI.

🎯 Objectives
Validate REST API endpoints (GET, POST, PUT, DELETE)
Verify response status codes and data integrity
Ensure backend functionality works as expected
Support scalable and maintainable test structure

🧰 Tech Stack
Playwright (.NET) → API request handling
xUnit → Test framework
C# → Programming language
Postgres SQL → DBMS 
